| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-4950 — Recovery Inhibition (bianlian)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: f4b60d9b-5b48-588d-9bf4-b039830f4ac7"
